                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "May be stacked with Fortitude for complete immunity to knockdown. Another option is the Vaykor Sydon which provides additional 50% knockdown resistance when wielded."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Sure Footed",
                  "pageId": 122560,
                  "revisionId": 2663929,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Includes resistance from Shield Lancer 's shield attack, Scorpion 's tether attack, Ancient 's charge attack and tether attack, Corpus Laser Barriers , Bombard rocket explosions and Arson / Caustic Eximus' fire blasts."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Sure Footed",
                  "pageId": 122560,
                  "revisionId": 2663929,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Despite being knockdown resistance, it also provides resistance to Volatile Runner 's explosions which stagger the player, rather than knocking down the player."
                }
              },
